Search for Neyrelle and the Horadric Vault
Search for Neyrelle in the Darkened Holt
I must search for Neyrelle in the Darkened Holt. Perhaps we can find the Horadric Vault together.
Neyrelle continued her search for the Horadric Vault in the Darkened Holt, a place known to swallow locals in its swirling, cold air and dense foliage. I must find her before it's too late.

Neyrelle was found none the worse for wear. I gather she is more resilient than people credit her for. It is time for us to leave this seemingly endless Horadric illusion. What that means for our search for the Horadric Vault, I am unsure.
